    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身公会修习的年轻盗贼，登上色彩缤纷的群岛，调查一桩桩绑架事件，直面或回避各地海盗。驾着可爱的海龟遨游海洋，踏上每一座海岛，治好生病的动物，发现舒心旅程背后的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《如风：盗贼之歌》致敬《超越善恶》和《塞尔达传说：风之杖》等经典冒险游戏，包含探索、对话、战斗、解谜、收集和大型头目对战等丰富元素，一切尽在发人深思而又舒心的缤纷世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索缤纷多彩的开放世界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344990/extras/369bec230b1c0776924d55befd4e635f.poster.avif?t=1770726239\" width=780 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344990/extras/369bec230b1c0776924d55befd4e635f.webm?t=1770726239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344990/extras/369bec230b1c0776924d55befd4e635f.mp4?t=1770726239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随便怎么跑、跳、爬都没有问题，驾着海龟往返各座海岛，探索这个缤纷的开放世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >正面对抗还是隐秘回避？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344990/extras/ef667b0d65502df3f48eedee1ce6fae1.poster.avif?t=1770726239\" width=780 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344990/extras/ef667b0d65502df3f48eedee1ce6fae1.webm?t=1770726239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344990/extras/ef667b0d65502df3f48eedee1ce6fae1.mp4?t=1770726239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论海盗、卫兵、机器人还是其他盗贼，都不会很好对付。你可以悄悄躲开他们，也可以上前正面战斗，随你选择，不过千万谨慎选择！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >强力头目</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344990/extras/002623cb2a1bd70150ee87ab7f5e0591.poster.avif?t=1770726239\" width=780 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344990/extras/002623cb2a1bd70150ee87ab7f5e0591.webm?t=1770726239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344990/extras/002623cb2a1bd70150ee87ab7f5e0591.mp4?t=1770726239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将在冒险途中遭遇古代守卫，有些会挡住你的去路，有些则非常隐蔽。你有能力让这些巨大的生物归于平静？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >支线任务</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344990/extras/5762577d52038b2a7d231a39cb630487.poster.avif?t=1770726239\" width=780 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344990/extras/5762577d52038b2a7d231a39cb630487.webm?t=1770726239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1344990/extras/5762577d52038b2a7d231a39cb630487.mp4?t=1770726239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找生病的动物，用水果治好他们的病！采摘花朵、发现遗失的画作……众多支线任务等你来完成，不知道你能不能全部找到。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由探索缤纷绚烂的开放世界。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >攀爬、潜行、战斗、弓箭、炸弹、抓钩等等各种技能可以学习！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直面或者回避海盗、卫兵和机器人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >治好世界各地生病的动物。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集宝石、画作和花朵。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >展开恢弘的战斗，击败巨大的护卫。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >邂逅可爱而又有趣的角色。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拯救世界！呃，不是，我意思是“成为真正的英雄”！呃，也不是，我意思是“救你妹妹”。嗐，反正你总要有个目标……</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >哦对！还有一头可爱的海龟可以骑！不过你应该已经在图片里看到了。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开发者简介</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大家好！我是Mathias，我从小就开发电子游戏，已经很多年了。我喜欢编程，喜欢写曲子，也喜欢画画，所以开发电子游戏让我有机会同时精进这三个爱好。游戏的所有工作都是我独立完成，因为我喜欢每一个环节，我也很喜欢了解各项工作！希望大家会喜欢这款游戏:）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要是想支持我或者进一步了解我，欢迎访问我的网站，能看到我所有社交账号，我的Patreon，开发日志和所有作品。非常感谢大家的支持！</p>",
